<br />
<br />PERFECT example:
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ieqs1zFr03k">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ieqs1zFr03k</a><!-- m -->

		

