<br />Well, in the PAL version this is worse - the whole screen completely flickers and this boss is almost unbeatable, and yes, using an official cartridge, official NES, etc... I even tried 2 different cartridges to be sure but the glitch is present in both of them.
<br />
<br />I guess they fixed this in the PRG1 verison (both cartridge I have are PRG0), but anyway THIS is innacetpable. I agree minor glitches are lame, but a major flicker that makes you unable to see what happens on the screen is REALLY inacceptable. Can't belive Nintnedo put their seal of squality on it.

		

